- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses constructing a symmetric monoidal double category, which involves organizing data in a structured way. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper mentions Nash and subgame perfect equilibria, which are concepts commonly used in AI research.
